    "## Start Load Test in Separate Terminal\n",
    "The params are as follows:\n",
    "* `$1: amount of load low|medium|high`\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "loadtest high\n",
    "\n",
    "### EXPECTED OUTPUT ###\n",
    "summary ... 38.6/s Avg:  1175 Min:    26 Max:  2320 Err:     0 (0.00%)\n",
